hopobject.body: Sorry, you must have the wrong number clindamycin preis Jack was concerned that, when it came to ATMs, too much emphasis was placed on the “physical” defences, such as whether the machine was bolted down, or whether there was CCTV. “This is the first time anyone had actually looked at the underlying software,” he claimed. “And once I sort of dug in, ripped the software apart, I was really surprised at the amount of flaws that are hiding underneath there.” He added: “I am not naive enough to think I am the only one who can do it.”
